<db:anchor xml:id="cmake-manual"/>
<db:para><db:code>CMake</db:code> is a tool to simplify the build process for development projects across different platforms. <db:code>CMake</db:code> automatically generates build systems, such as Makefiles and Ninja files.</db:para>
<db:para><db:code>CMake</db:code> is a third-party tool with its own <db:link xlink:href="http://www.cmake.org/cmake/help/documentation.html">documentation</db:link>. This manual focuses on how to use <db:code>CMake</db:code> to build Qt applications and libraries.</db:para>
